title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger
description:
This is seven episodes of the Lone Ranger cartoon from the early 80's. I am not a master at uploading videos or anything so don't be upset if it's not perfect, I've never done this before. I simply ripped a DVD I have and then made a torrent out of it. For some reason though, something I did, made the third episode breakdown by chapter.


Otherwise....enjoy.
